SUMMARY:Collector’s Lunch Pairing at Lynmar Estate
DESCRIPTION:Quail Hill Vineyard Collector's Lunch Paring Experience at Lynmar Estate is available March 19 - November 1 from 12:30 am to 2:30 pm\, offering a luxurious wine and food pairing in the beautiful setting of Quail Hill Vineyard. Guests will enjoy an elevated multi-course lunch thoughtfully paired with ultra-premium Pinot Noir and Chardonnay from the estate.    During the experience\, Estate Chef David Frakes will make a special tableside visit\, adding a personal touch to this immersive culinary journey. Surrounded by vineyard views\, the experience highlights the connection between seasonal ingredients\, exceptional wines\, and the unique terroir of the estate.    Reservations are required\, and group sizes are limited to a maximum of six guests to ensure an intimate and personalized experience.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/collectors-lunch-pairing-at-lynmar-estate/
LOCATION:3909 Frei Rd, Sebastopol, CA, 95472, United States
GEO:-122.8445728;38.4421027
CATEGORIES:Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Sonoma County,Wine
