SUMMARY:Wine &amp; Dine with Coursey Graves and Songbird Parlour
DESCRIPTION:Coursey Graves invites guests to its Wine and Dine series\, pairing three 2023 wines Chardonnay\, Pinot Noir\, and Cabernet Sauvignon with five seasonal courses. Attendees will hear from the winemakers as they share the story and craft behind each bottle. Perched 1\,500 feet above Sonoma Valley\, Coursey Graves combines panoramic views\, artful gardens\, and a commitment to exceptional farming and winemaking\, creating a memorable tasting experience. Space is limited.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/wine-dine-with-coursey-graves-and-songbird-parlour/
LOCATION:14301 Arnold Dr #3, Glen Ellen, CA, 95442, United States
CATEGORIES:Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Sonoma County,Wine
