SUMMARY:Winter Food Truck Pop-Up at Gehricke Tasting Room
DESCRIPTION:Cousins Maine Lobster is returning to Gehricke Tasting Room for a Winter Food Truck Pop-Up. Get ready for a taste of the coast with their famous lobster rolls\, chowder\, and seafood favorites. Fresh\, buttery\, and packed with flavor\, it’s the perfect pairing with a glass of Chardonnay.    Located in Sonoma’s historic firehouse just steps from the square\, Gehricke Tasting Room pours small-lot wines made with minimal intervention so you can enjoy the truest representation of each appellation.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/winter-food-truck-pop-up-at-gehricke-tasting-room-2/
LOCATION:32 Patten Street, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
CATEGORIES:Dining,Drink,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Sonoma County,Wine
