SUMMARY:Sonoma International Film Festival
DESCRIPTION:Set in the valley’s springtime beauty\, the Sonoma International Film Festival welcomes filmmakers and cinephiles to a five-day celebration of storytelling and cinema from March 25th - 29th. From Sonoma’s historic plaza to surrounding vineyards\, the event offers screenings\, culinary experiences\, and wine pairings that highlight the region’s creative and agricultural spirit.    Films are shown in the historic Sebastiani Theatre\, a 91-year-old venue that evokes a timeless cinematic experience and the simple pleasures of shared stories. Guests are invited to explore a curated program of films that inspire connection and conversation\, paired with the exceptional flavors and hospitality of wine country.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/sonoma-international-film-festival/
LOCATION:783 Broadway, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
GEO:-122.459041;38.286879
CATEGORIES:Arts,Celebration,Fairs & Festivals,Film,Food,Food & Wine,Food and Wine Pairing,Wine
