SUMMARY:Elevated Sessions at The Lounge at Mercy
DESCRIPTION:Elevated Sessions is an intimate\, sommelier-led cannabis tasting designed for discerning enthusiasts. Guests will explore premium indoor flower from Mercy Grown during a guided 60‑minute experience focused on aroma\, terpene profiles\, flavor\, and effects. A knowledgeable cannabis sommelier leads the tasting of four curated cultivars while guests enjoy natural sodas\, curated snacks\, charcuterie\, and palate cleansers.    The evening features two sessions with limited seating to ensure a refined and personal atmosphere. Each guest receives a tasting passport to record notes and preferences\, along with the opportunity to meet the grower and learn about the craft behind the award‑winning flower.    Tickets include the guided tasting\, snacks\, natural soda bar\, exclusive perks\, and a $50 goodie bag. Capacity is limited\, creating a relaxed and immersive experience for cannabis connoisseurs. 21+ only.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/elevated-sessions-at-the-lounge-at-mercy-2/
LOCATION:7950 Redwood Dr, , Cotati, CA, 94931, United States
CATEGORIES:Food,Sonoma County,Tastings
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/03/09233934/Elevated-Sessions-February-500-x-500-Sesh-in-Action-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
